### 2. Commercial License (4% Gross Revenue)

**For:** For-profit companies, commercial enterprises, and businesses generating revenue from this software.

**Terms:**
- **Revenue Share:** 4% of gross revenue derived from or facilitated by this software
- **Minimum Threshold:** Revenue share applies when gross revenue exceeds $10,000 USD annually
- **Payment:** Annual payment due within 60 days of fiscal year end
- **Reporting:** Annual revenue report required

**Eligibility (REQUIRED for):**
- For-profit corporations, LLCs, partnerships
- Commercial SaaS providers using FoodSecurityNet
- Consulting firms deploying FoodSecurityNet for clients
- Agriculture technology companies integrating FoodSecurityNet
- Any entity generating revenue from FoodSecurityNet-powered services

**License Text:** See [LICENSE-COMMERCIAL](LICENSE-COMMERCIAL)

