## Registration & Compliance

### Non-Profit Users

To use the Non-Profit License, you must:
1. Register at: https://license.foodsecuritynet.org/nonprofit
2. Provide proof of non-profit status (tax exemption letter, charity registration)
3. Receive license confirmation (usually within 3 business days)
4. Renew annually (free, just confirm continued non-profit status)

**Registration is FREE and takes 5 minutes.**

### Commercial Users

To use the Commercial License, you must:
1. Register at: https://license.foodsecuritynet.org/commercial
2. Complete commercial license agreement
3. Provide company information and billing details
4. Receive license key and agreement
5. Submit annual revenue reports
6. Pay revenue share annually

**Get started with a 90-day trial period** - no fees for first 90 days!

